---
title: Cheesy Beef & Corn Enchiladas with Mixed Salad & Sour Cream
description: Everyone loves enchiladas, but we've made them even more lovable by getting them on the table quicker. This version
uses the grill to melt the cheese, and adds corn and carrot to the beef mixture for extra flavour and texture.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/cheats-beef-corn-enchiladas-35c5fc90.jpg
